<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>أَفَلاا يَتَدَبَّرُونَ الْقُرْآنَ* <span class="c2">«٣»</span>.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
